@startuml
title Terminal management between a TMS and a POI (catm)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E7EAEE
  BorderColor #4A5A70
}
skinparam ArrowColor #4A5A70
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E7EAEE
skinparam noteBorderColor #4A5A70

[POI\n(payment terminal)] as POI
[Terminal management\nsystem (TMS)] as TMS

POI --> TMS : catm.001 Status Report
TMS --> POI : catm.002 Management Plan Replacement
TMS --> POI : catm.003 Acceptor Configuration Update
TMS --> POI : catm.007 Certificate Management Request
POI --> TMS : catm.008 Certificate Management Response
note bottom of TMS : catm manages the terminal;\ncaaa carries its transactions
@enduml
